me.Ninjoh.NinCore

Class Tick

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.Ninjoh.NinCore.Tick

  • public class Tick
extends java.lang.Object
    WARNING: Ticks to time calculations are based on 20 ticks per second. Ideally Minecraft has 20 ticks per seconds. But with lag it CAN be less than 20 ticks per second and thus these calculations will not be accurate when Minecraft does not have 20 ticks per second.
